data.title: Living Faith World Ministries
data.meta_description: We are a non-denominational church that quite simply believes in lifting up the name of Jesus Christ and changing lives through the Word of God. There is something for everyone here! The faces of Living Faith World Ministries tell many stories.
data.text:
Pastor Sharlene and I are excited that you have chosen to explore our website and spend some quality time with us. It is our hope that as you journey through this site you find opportunities for spiritual enrichment, educational development, and the tools to empower you to reach the next dimension in your life! ​ Living Faith World Ministries, Inc. is a Christian church nestled on a 6-acre piece of land in the middle of a historic community in Daytona Beach, Florida. However, our light shines bright as we are committed to

taking the Gospel of Jesus Christ to the world through evangelism, mission work, and community outreach. ​ We are here for you! Pastor Sharlene, myself, and the Living Faith Church family invite you to worship, fellowship, and grow with us. Here at Living Faith, we walk in expectation and are excited about what God is doing in the kingdom! ​ We hope you believe as we believe; “The best is yet to come!” ​ Yours in Christ, ​ Apostle Tony and Pastor Sharlene Barhoo.

There is no better time or reason to wait. Download your copy of the one-year scripture reading and start your learning today. You can also download the Free Bible App by YouVersion from your mobile device and subscribe to the One Year Bible reading plan so you can read the word of God from anywhere.

The message of Living Faith World Ministries is that together we will build, expand, and enlarge the Kingdom of God through His power, love and compassion for all humanity. Therefore, we must preach and teach the gospel of Jesus Christ to all who seek His Word.
